    "Each query was repeated three times in each tool to assess within-platform variability.",
    "We also accessed the tools through different browsers.",
    "Each response was coded separately for a total of 30 per tool.",
    "Queries were made between February and May 2024 from New York City.",
    "A set of features related to usability and quality (i.e., is the information provided helpful and is it communicated in a sensitive way?)"
